Where Can My Robot Go? (EASY)

CTF Platform: CTFLearn

Category: Web Exploitation
Objective: Find the hidden flag by exploring the robots.txt file.

Approach
  The hint mentioned “robots,” which typically refers to the robots.txt file. This file, located at the root of a website, instructs web crawlers which directories are allowed or disallowed for indexing.

Steps
  Navigate to https://ctflearn.com/robots.txt

  The file listed a disallowed directory:
      - Disallow: /70r3hnanldfspufdsoifnlds.html

Visit the disallowed path:
      - https://ctflearn.com/__________________.html

Flag
flag{robots_are_cool} ## Not actual flag ##
